TITLE: Installing Tools via Pre-processor Directive in Cake CSharp
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use the #tool pre-processor directive in a Cake build script to automatically download and install an external tool (xunit.runner.console) from NuGet. There are no external code dependencies beyond Cake itself, and the URI string specifies the package source and version. The directive is parsed by Cake at build time and downloads the tool into the 'tools' directory for use during script execution.
SOURCE: https://github.com/cake-build/website/blob/master/input/docs/writing-builds/tools/installing-tools.md#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
#tool \"nuget:?package=xunit.runner.console&version=2.4.1\"
```

