TITLE: Sending Email via SMTP Server using Cake.Email Addin in C#
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to send an email using the Cake.Email addin. It connects to an SMTP server (Gmail in this example) and sends an HTML email. The code includes error handling and reports the success or failure of the email sending operation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/cake-build/website/blob/master/input/blog/2016-10-31-email-addins-released.md#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
