TITLE: Pinning Tool Version via PackageReference in Cake Frosting (XML)
DESCRIPTION: Illustrates how to pin a specific version (1.2.3) of a tool ('Tool.Foo') consumed as a NuGet package within a Cake Frosting project. This is done by adding a standard `<PackageReference>` element with a specific `Version` attribute to the project's `.csproj` file, leveraging MSBuild/NuGet's dependency management.
SOURCE: https://github.com/cake-build/website/blob/master/input/docs/writing-builds/reproducible-builds/pinning-tool-version.md#2025-04-23_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: xml
CODE:
```
<PackageReference Include="Tool.Foo" Version="1.2.3" />
```

