TITLE: Collection Initializers in Cake - After Enhancement
DESCRIPTION: Example showing the improved collection initializer syntax that eliminates the need for explicit dictionary instantiation, making code more concise.
SOURCE: https://github.com/cake-build/website/blob/master/input/blog/2018-08-22-cake-v0.30.0-released.md#2025-04-23_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
new FooToolSettings
{
    EnvironmentVariables = { ["FOO"] = "foo" }
}
```

