TITLE: Finding Installations with Specific Components
DESCRIPTION: Example of finding Visual Studio installations that have specific components installed
SOURCE: https://github.com/cake-build/website/blob/master/input/blog/2017-03-27-vswhere-and-visual-studio-2017-support.md#2025-04-23_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
#tool nuget:?package=vswhere

DirectoryPathCollection allInstalled  = VSWhereAll(new VSWhereAllSettings { Requires = "Microsoft.Component.MSBuild" });

foreach(var install in allInstalled)
{
    // Find the installation you need
}
```

