TITLE: Configuring Cake NuGet Client in Config File
DESCRIPTION: Specifies configuration in a Cake config file to disable the in-process NuGet client. This provides an alternative method to opt out of the new default behavior.
SOURCE: https://github.com/cake-build/website/blob/master/input/blog/2018-01-17-cake-v0.25.0-released.md#2025-04-23_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: sh
CODE:
```
